        "C": "(AB)⁻¹ = A⁻¹B⁻¹",
        "D": "(A+B)ᵀ = Aᵀ - Bᵀ"
      },
      "answer": "A",
      "pyq": false
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "question": "For a non-singular matrix A, the inverse A⁻¹ is given by ______.",
